                  <summary>
                    Miniatures added in the late 20th century by the "Speckled Garment Artist". ‎
                    Decorative designs for section dividers <locus target = "#1r #35r #69r #103v #114v #‎‎120v"/>(elaborate haräg using black, red, yellow and green);
                    many ‎folios employ line of alternating red and black dots <locus target = "#6v #12v #19v #‎‎28v #40r #47v #57r #64r #79v #90r #92v #98r #121r #126v #130r #‎‎134v"/>;
                    others employ a series of full-stop symbols <locus target = "#123r #‎‎124v"/>. ‎
                    </summary>
