                   <additions>
                     <list>
                       <item xml:id="e1">
                         <locus target = "iv(erso)"/>
                         <desc>Record of a debt of three schillings, including witnesses; written in ‎ink pen by a later hand. ‎</desc>
                       </item>
                       <item xml:id = "e2">
                         <locus target = "iiv(erso)"/>
                         <desc>a list of the Gǝ‘ǝz alphabet and numbers, in black ink.‎</desc>
                         </item>
                      <item xml:id = "e3">
                        <locus target = "iiv(erso)"/>
                        <desc>‎List of the astrological signs. ‎</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id = "a1">
                          <locus target = "135v"/>
                          <desc>Excerpt from Computus, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3851Hassab"></ref>, how Dǝmeṭros found the calculation of the epact <foreign xml:lang = "gez">‎የጥንተ፡ አብቅቴ፡ ይትመጣ፡ ድሜጥሮስ፡ በመዓልት፡ ፯፡ ሱባዔ፡ በሌሊት፡‎</foreign>.
                        </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id = "e4">
                          <locus target = "iv(erso)"/>
                            <desc>Title of the book in pencil</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id = "e5">
                        <locus target = "#ir #iir"/>
                          <desc>Blank</desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id = "e6">
                            <locus target = "#103v"/>
                            <desc type = "OwnershipNote">Upper margin, name of owner <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ ሃና፡</foreign></desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id = "e7">
                            <locus target = "#136v"/>
                            <desc>Prepared to receive painting, but never completed‎.</desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id = "e8">
                            <desc>Scribal intervention: words of text are written interlinearly <locus target = "#24v #60r #99v #120v #133r #135v"/>;
                            and ‎lines of text are written interlinearly <locus target = "#11v #15v #69v #94v"/>;
                            and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) ‎in red and black ink marking the location where the text is to be inserted <locus target = "#129v"/>, line 4 and <locus target = "#133r"/>, line ‎‎16);
                            erasure markings are visible <locus target = "#59v"/>; text has been removed <locus target = "#51r #65v #100v"/>‎</desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id = "e9">
                            <desc>‎12.‎	The scribe regularly has to complete a line of text on another line.
                              ‎Much of the problem is addressed through the selection of an ‎appropriate aspect ratio for the
                              codex combined with an appropriate ‎script size.
                              But, where the line of text is still too long, the scribe ‎completes the line of text above or below
                              the end of the line ‎‎(throughout). This scribe also will reduce the font size at the end of ‎lines to avoid
                              having to go onto the next line (e.g., <locus target = "#19v #20r"/>).‎</desc>
                          </item>

                        </list>
                     </additions>
